## Attribution Note

This is a port of [anthropics/claude-desktop-buddy](https://github.com/anthropics/claude-desktop-buddy)
(originally targeting M5StickC Plus 1 hardware) to the M5StickS3 hardware
(ESP32-S3 + 8 MB PSRAM + ES8311 audio codec).

The upstream copyright (Anthropic, PBC.) is preserved per the original MIT
License above. The clawstick contributors' copyright covers the M5StickS3-
specific port adaptations including:

- M5Unified API migration (replacing M5StickCPlus library)
- ESP32-S3 / AXP2101 / M5PM1 / BMI270 / ES8311 hardware adaptation
- USB-CDC native protocol (replacing UART bridge)
- S3-only extensions (PSRAM character cache, audio cue, bilingual UI)
- Accompanying documentation (UPSTREAM-DELTA.md, README, gotchas)
